txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Pure black skin from the beasts and worms surrounding Sûri-kylä. Deliver the items to Kaleva at the Lossoth capital.
'We will make use of these. Thank you.'
'The beasts and worms leave their skin for our hunters. Perhaps they will leave them for you.'
A Lossoth, Kaleva, at Sûri-kylä is collecting pure black skin at the Lossoth capital.
Deliver the pure black skin to Kaleva at Sûri-kylä in Forochel
You have accepted a task to collect and deliver pure black skin from the beasts and worms surrounding Sûri-kylä in Forochel. The items are to be delivered to Kaleva at the Lossoth capital.
Wanted: Pure black skin from the beasts and worms surrounding Sûri-kylä.
